This product bundles the following third-party assets:

- ONNX Runtime (Microsoft, MIT). Linked via `ort` crate when the
  `onnx-bundled` feature is enabled.
- sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (Apache-2.0). Bundled tokenizer
  + ONNX export from `Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2`.
- Other Rust crates per the workspace Cargo.lock; license texts of all
  transitive dependencies are reproduced in `THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md`
  (regenerated on each release via `cargo about`).
